Gateway Changelog
=================

Here you can see the full list of changes between each Flask release.

Version 0.2
-----------
Released on October 14th 2012

Features
~~~~~~~~

* add the __format__ attribute on the Converter, it able to use a native or a json stream.
  with this way, you can use curl or httpie to post a http for some tests


Fixes:
~~~~~~

* fix the format of the datetime in examples/client.py

Version 0.1
-----------

Released on September 30th 2012, codename Started

First public preview release.
